{"questionId":"10024","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let <strong><em>A</em> </strong>=&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  a&amp;b \\\\   c&amp;0  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>a</mi>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>b</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>c</mi>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> and <strong><em>B</em> </strong>=&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1&amp;0 \\\\   d&amp;e  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>d</mi>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>e</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>. Giving your answers in terms of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n</math></span>, <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"b\">\n  <mi>b</mi>\n</math></span>, <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"c\">\n  <mi>c</mi>\n</math></span>, <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"d\">\n  <mi>d</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp;and <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"e\">\n  <mi>e</mi>\n</math></span>,</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>write down <strong><em>A</em> </strong>+<strong> <em>B</em></strong>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p style=\"color:#999;font-size:90%;font-style:italic;\">* This question is from an exam for a previous syllabus, and may contain minor differences in marking or structure.</p>\n<p><strong><em>A</em></strong> + <strong><em>B</em></strong> =&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  a&amp;b \\\\   c&amp;0  \\end{array}} \\right) + \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1&amp;0 \\\\   d&amp;e  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>a</mi>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>b</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>c</mi>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>d</mi>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>e</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {a + 1}&amp;b \\\\   {c + d}&amp;e  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              